40
00:05:08,174 --> 00:05:10,802
Hey !
You lookin'forsomethin' ?

41
00:05:10,877 --> 00:05:15,405
Huh, hey !. Howdy-hey there, boy.
Ha-ha-ha. Name is Halverson.

42
