Lloyd Halverson.
Ha-ha.

43
00:05:18,518 --> 00:05:21,817
I-I hate the name, so you
can just use what you like.

44
00:05:23,790 --> 00:05:28,557
Now the, uh, wolfhere,
I recollect him vividly. Ha-ha-ha.

45
00:05:28,628 --> 00:05:31,995
