about a year ago this time.

54
00:06:00,493 --> 00:06:03,053
I s he, uh...
he your brother ?.

55
00:06:03,129 --> 00:06:07,691
Friend. He left me in charge
of his claim.

56
00:06:09,502 --> 00:06:11,868
