260
00:28:51,696 --> 00:28:55,632
This is very good.
Welcome to ourvillage.

261
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:58,897
I am Moses Joseph,
chief ofthe Haidas.

262
00:29:00,371 --> 00:29:03,499
Henry Casey.
San Francisco.

263
00:29:04,576 --> 00:29:08,307
Henry Casey.
Casey Henry.

264
00:29:08,379 --> 00:29:11,075
Funny name.

265
00:29:11,149 --> 00:29:13,083
Thankyou.

266
00:29:13,151 --> 00:29:15,085
Come.

267
00:29:16,154 --> 00:29:18,247
[ Haida Language ]

268
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:23,087
%% [ Chanting ]

269
00:29:41,913 --> 00:29:43,847
[ Sniffing ]

270
00:29:47,886 --> 00:29:49,820
[ Sniffing ]

271
00:30:24,522 --> 00:30:26,456
[ Coughs ]

272
00:30:39,838 --> 00:30:42,068
At the time of my
grandfather's grandfather,

273
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:46,201
our mother, the earth, shook,

274
00:30:46,277 --> 00:30:51,010
and part ofthe mountain
you call Devil's Thumb broke off.

275
00:30:51,082 --> 00:30:55,610
Many ofourpeople died,
but in return,

276
00:30:55,687 --> 00:30:58,451
the Creator gave us
the caribou.

277
00:30:58,523 --> 00:31:03,085
Eachyear they come to us
from Devil's Thumb.

278
00:31:03,161 --> 00:31:08,497
For this reason, we respect
the mountain and do not go there.

279
00:31:10,201 --> 00:31:13,329
For two years now,
the caribou have not returned.

280
00:31:13,404 --> 00:31:15,964
Eight hunters went to find them.

281
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,974
They, too, have vanished.

282
00:31:19,077 --> 00:31:21,102
Without the caribou...

283
00:31:21,179 --> 00:31:24,808
the balance in our lives
is gone.

284
00:31:24,883 --> 00:31:29,752
Without this balance,
my people...

285
00:31:29,821 --> 00:31:32,255
slowlystarve,

286
00:31:32,323 --> 00:31:37,386
die, move away.

287
00:31:37,462 --> 00:31:41,023
Ifmy dream showed me
the way ofthis god-man,

288
00:31:41,099 --> 00:31:44,398
I would ask my people
to move.

289
00:31:44,469 --> 00:31:48,769
But the dream
told ofthe wolf...

290
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:50,808
that would lead us
to the caribou.

291
00:31:50,875 --> 00:31:55,073
And now, Henry Casey,
you are here.

292
00:31:57,015 --> 00:31:59,245
Me ?.

293
00:32:03,621 --> 00:32:06,749
Got the wrong man, sir.

294
00:32:06,824 --> 00:32:10,658
I'm not much ofa hunter.
I'm more ofa miner.

295
00:32:13,231 --> 00:32:15,756
That is very interesting.

296
00:32:15,833 --> 00:32:18,267
Really.

297
00:32:21,339 --> 00:32:23,933
That wolfyour niece
saw me with...

298
00:32:24,008 --> 00:32:26,943
was a pet.

299
00:32:27,011 --> 00:32:30,071
He's the hunter.

300
00:32:31,916 --> 00:32:34,043
He was something.

301
00:32:35,119 --> 00:32:37,212
But he's gone now.

302
00:32:37,288 --> 00:32:41,725
He could be alive insideyou.
The wolfhas the power to change.

303
00:32:41,793 --> 00:32:43,954
Into me.

304
00:32:46,965 --> 00:32:50,594
I guess that's okay
to believe, sir,

305
00:32:50,668 --> 00:32:52,602
but I don't.

306
00:32:54,339 --> 00:32:56,705
I'm no wolf.

307
00:32:56,774 --> 00:32:58,571
[ Laughing ]

308
00:32:58,643 --> 00:33:01,134
- [All Chuckle ]
- I'm a man.

309
00:33:04,849 --> 00:33:06,783
That's all.

310
00:33:06,851 --> 00:33:10,981
[ Laughter Continues ]

311
00:33:27,238 --> 00:33:29,502
This boy is free to leave
when he wishes.

312
00:33:32,710 --> 00:33:34,678
Thankyou.

313
00:33:34,746 --> 00:33:39,376
I need supplies. I need to wire
San Francisco for some money.

314
00:33:39,450 --> 00:33:41,782
There must be
a town near here.

315
00:33:41,853 --> 00:33:44,185
When you are ready,
we can showyou the way.

316
00:33:44,255 --> 00:33:48,919
Ifit's all right with you, I'll stay
here tonight. I'll leave in the morning.

317
00:33:48,993 --> 00:33:54,090
Good idea. Katrin can showyou
where to lay down.

318
00:33:54,165 --> 00:33:56,360
Sleep now, Casey Henry.

319
00:33:59,070 --> 00:34:03,598
- We can talk again tomorrow.
- Okay.

320
00:34:03,674 --> 00:34:06,837
[ Chuckling ]
He's a nice old guy, huh ?.

321
00:34:08,479 --> 00:34:11,539
Old guy is my father.

322
00:34:11,616 --> 00:34:14,744
- Who areyou in his house ?.
- I didn't mean anything.

323
00:34:14,819 --> 00:34:18,084
Henry, this way.

324
00:34:34,839 --> 00:34:37,273
White Fang.

325
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:46,407
I should have known.
You don't see.

326
00:34:46,484 --> 00:34:49,476
I didn't askyou
to bring me here.

327
00:34:51,489 --> 00:34:56,188
- I sang the healing song foryou.
- What's that supposed to mean ?.

328
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:58,751
I gaveyou backyour life.

329
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:05,232
Doyou believe that stuff ?.

330
00:35:08,039 --> 00:35:10,769
All you believe in
is your gold.

331
00:35:14,112 --> 00:35:17,843
I'm grateful
whatyou did for me.

332
00:35:21,419 --> 00:35:25,014
But I'm not gonna go to some
godforsaken place to hunt caribou.

333
00:35:25,089 --> 00:35:27,319
We thoughtyou were the wolf.

334
00:35:28,926 --> 00:35:30,860
Sorry.

335
00:35:30,928 --> 00:35:35,991
The wolfis a great hunter
with a warrior's heart.

336
00:35:36,067 --> 00:35:39,002
You are like every other
white man.

337
00:35:59,790 --> 00:36:03,783
Follow the river.
Before darkyou will come to it.

338
00:36:54,812 --> 00:36:57,144
- Major.
- [ Reverend ] You shouldn't be here.

339
00:36:57,215 --> 00:36:59,445
I told you not to--
[ Indistinct ]

340
00:36:59,517 --> 00:37:01,883
[Reverend]
Followme.

341
00:37:01,953 --> 00:37:05,616
- Yes, sir. Hyah !
- Let's go. Hyah !

342
00:37:26,577 --> 00:37:29,102
Morning ! Hi, there.

343
00:37:42,994 --> 00:37:46,293
[Henry] I figured
the best thing to do is keep movin'.

344
00:37:46,364 --> 00:37:49,993
- At least I wouldn't
be eatin' their food.
- [ Horses Whinnying ]

345
00:37:50,067 --> 00:37:52,297
Then Lily,

346
00:37:52,370 --> 00:37:55,032
the I ndian gi rl--

347
00:37:56,741 --> 00:37:59,232
She walked me to the stream
and pointed me here.

348
00:38:00,311 --> 00:38:03,280
Why didn't you stay
and help them ?.

349
00:38:03,347 --> 00:38:08,148
Why ?. I'll tell you why.
You're Indian, right ?.

350
00:38:11,389 --> 00:38:15,951
I thought so. Soyou probably
understand them a bit better than I do.

351
00:38:16,027 --> 00:38:19,224
They believe...
s-strange things up there.

352
00:38:19,297 --> 00:38:22,289
Like their dreams.

353
00:38:22,366 --> 00:38:24,596
They need help.

354
00:38:27,171 --> 00:38:31,130
I thought I saw some soldiers
while I was comin' in.
Where are they quartered ?.

355
00:38:31,208 --> 00:38:33,904
The army's in Dawson.

356
00:38:33,978 --> 00:38:36,105
Huh-uh.
No, I just saw them.

357
00:38:38,549 --> 00:38:41,279
You just saw somebody
passin' through.

358
00:38:42,620 --> 00:38:44,747
So nowyou'll go home...

359
00:38:44,822 --> 00:38:47,382
and forget these people
who helped you.

360
00:38:47,458 --> 00:38:52,418
IfI thought
I could help them, I would.

361
00:38:52,496 --> 00:38:55,863
- They thinkyou can.
- They think I'm the white wolf.

362
00:38:56,934 --> 00:38:58,868
Maybeyou are.

363
00:39:06,010 --> 00:39:09,946
[ Conversing In
Haida Language]

364
00:39:20,191 --> 00:39:24,491
That's him, Uncle.
That's thewolf.

365
00:39:26,330 --> 00:39:29,891
[Moses]
The otherhalf. It's a goodsign.

366
00:39:31,936 --> 00:39:33,870
Good sign.

367
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:06,400
Don't be afraid, my brother.
Don't be afraid.

368
00:40:30,127 --> 00:40:32,061
[ Baby Crying ]

369
00:40:55,653 --> 00:40:58,952
[ Coughing ]

370
00:41:21,545 --> 00:41:23,604
Sad, isn't it ?.

371
00:41:40,331 --> 00:41:43,494
[Whooshing]

372
00:41:46,303 --> 00:41:48,737
%% [Drum ]

373
00:41:58,816 --> 00:42:02,252
%% [ Continues ]

374
00:42:51,936 --> 00:42:54,302
[Eagle Crying]

375
00:43:03,814 --> 00:43:06,248
%% [Stops ]

376
00:43:20,831 --> 00:43:22,765
I'm goin' back.

377
00:43:45,856 --> 00:43:47,790
[ Yips ]

378
00:43:50,661 --> 00:43:52,856
[ Whines ]

379
00:43:56,433 --> 00:43:58,162
[ Growling ]

380
00:44:00,270 --> 00:44:02,204
[ Whines ]

381
00:44:07,344 --> 00:44:09,335
Gentlemen.

382
00:44:10,614 --> 00:44:12,582
Was there any mail for me yesterday,
Mr. Hale ?.

383
00:44:12,650 --> 00:44:16,177
- One for Rev. Michael.
- Uh, I'll take that.

384
00:44:16,253 --> 00:44:18,187
How long you figure ?.

385
00:44:18,255 --> 00:44:22,021
Telegram will be there
in two, three days at the most.

386
00:44:22,092 --> 00:44:25,459
Ofcourse, whenyourmoney comes back
is anotherstory.

387
00:44:25,529 --> 00:44:27,724
[Hale ]
At least a week, maybe more.

388
00:44:27,798 --> 00:44:31,564
Can I get some credit ?.
I'm leavin' for the village tomorrow.

389
00:44:31,635 --> 00:44:34,069
I was hopin' to
take some food out there.

390
00:44:34,138 --> 00:44:37,665
Sorry, kid. No credit.

391
00:44:37,741 --> 00:44:41,404
I'll pay for it, Mr. Heath.
Give him what he wants.

392
00:44:41,478 --> 00:44:44,072
All right.

393
00:44:47,017 --> 00:44:48,951
I'm Leland Drury.

394
00:44:49,019 --> 00:44:54,013
- Henry Casey.
- I couldn't help but overhear.

395
00:44:54,091 --> 00:44:56,685
I go to the village often.
Their suffering is hard to ignore.

396
00:44:56,760 --> 00:44:59,524
I have some mules
that know the way,

397
00:44:59,596 --> 00:45:01,962
ifyou'd care to use one.

398
00:45:02,032 --> 00:45:04,933
Yeah, thanks.

399
00:45:05,002 --> 00:45:07,630
You're savin' me a trip.

400
00:45:14,244 --> 00:45:16,178
Walks like a soldier.

401
00:45:17,514 --> 00:45:19,448
Protestant.

402
00:45:47,211 --> 00:45:50,044
[Underbrush Crackling]

403
00:45:52,783 --> 00:45:55,251
[ Grunts ]

404
00:46:20,110 --> 00:46:22,271
[ Whimpers ]

405
00:47:23,807 --> 00:47:26,674
You understand the problem.
I want him out ofthe way !

406
00:47:26,743 --> 00:47:29,007
Do it now !

407
00:47:29,079 --> 00:47:31,240
All right.

408
00:47:46,864 --> 00:47:48,798
[Mule Brays ]

409
00:47:59,343 --> 00:48:01,607
[Mule Brays ]

410
00:48:03,213 --> 00:48:07,377
[ Braying ]

411
00:48:12,956 --> 00:48:16,187
[ Gun Clicking ]

412
00:49:34,671 --> 00:49:37,105
This is foryou.

413
00:49:45,315 --> 00:49:47,249
Whywould I wear this ?.

414
00:49:47,317 --> 00:49:50,980
I don't know.
I thought it would look pretty.

415
00:49:51,054 --> 00:49:53,147
Pretty like a white girl ?.

416
00:49:55,359 --> 00:50:00,296
No. Tell you what.
Don't wear it.

417
00:50:00,364 --> 00:50:03,527
See ifI care.
Here, give it back.

418
00:50:03,600 --> 00:50:08,401
What do I have to do ?
Look, I'm here !

419
00:50:08,472 --> 00:50:10,633
And I came back
to find those caribou,

420
00:50:10,707 --> 00:50:12,937
whetheryou
believe me or not.

421
00:50:13,010 --> 00:50:15,274
Maybe one ofthese days
when this is all over,

422
00:50:15,345 --> 00:50:17,711
you'll realize I 'm not as worthless
as you think I am.

423
00:50:17,781 --> 00:50:21,182
Henry Casey.

424
00:50:21,251 --> 00:50:23,412
- He was here looking foryou.
- Who was ?.

425
00:50:23,487 --> 00:50:25,921
The wolf.

426
00:50:27,224 --> 00:50:31,285
- White Fang ?. He's alive ?.
- Yeah.

427
00:50:31,361 --> 00:50:34,728
- Are you sure it was him ?.
- Same wolf.

428
00:50:34,798 --> 00:50:39,667
- Well, where is he ?. Where'd he go ?.
- Be patient. He will find you.

429
00:50:39,736 --> 00:50:45,197
Lily. Go find Katrin.
Tonight we do the ceremony.

430
00:51:14,797 --> 00:51:18,062
Mr. Heath ?

431
00:51:26,142 --> 00:51:29,236
He's just a boy, Leland.

432
00:51:29,312 --> 00:51:31,803
That boy could ruin
everything.

433
00:51:34,651 --> 00:51:37,415
Do I have to do
everything myself ?.

434
00:51:38,588 --> 00:51:41,318
%% [ Chanting In
Haida Language ]

435
00:51:52,101 --> 00:51:54,433
I shouldn't be down here.

436
00:51:54,504 --> 00:51:56,699
Let the wolf
inside you free.

437
00:51:56,773 --> 00:52:00,004
%% [ Continues ]

438
00:52:33,476 --> 00:52:37,310
%% [ Continues ]

439
00:52:38,381 --> 00:52:40,679
[ WolfHowling]

440
00:52:41,751 --> 00:52:43,685
%% [Stops ]

441
00:52:43,753 --> 00:52:47,519
[Howling Continues ]

442
00:52:47,590 --> 00:52:51,321
[ Villagers Muttering]

443
00:52:51,394 --> 00:52:53,760
That's White Fang.

444
00:52:53,830 --> 00:52:56,390
Go. Go.

445
00:53:30,833 --> 00:53:33,165
White Fang ?.

446
00:53:40,143 --> 00:53:42,168
Wait here.

447
00:53:55,825 --> 00:53:57,918
White Fang ?.

448
00:54:01,030 --> 00:54:03,055
Is that you, boy ?.

449
00:54:09,772 --> 00:54:11,933
- White Fang.
- [ Snarling, Barking ]

450
00:54:12,008 --> 00:54:14,340
Aah !

451
00:54:14,410 --> 00:54:17,174
- Hyeh ! Hah !
- [ Snarling ]

452
00:54:17,246 --> 00:54:19,976
- Hyah !
- [ Snarling, Barking ]

453
00:54:20,049 --> 00:54:22,381
- Hyah !
- [ Barking ]

454
00:54:22,451 --> 00:54:24,442
White Fang !

455
00:54:26,389 --> 00:54:30,416
[Whimpering]

456
00:54:36,966 --> 00:54:40,367
White Fang !
Come on, boy !

457
00:54:44,674 --> 00:54:47,006
You found a friend.

458
00:54:49,545 --> 00:54:51,672
Wow.

459
00:54:51,747 --> 00:54:54,272
[Moses ]
Henry Casey !

460
00:54:56,519 --> 00:54:58,510
Moses.

461
00:54:59,589 --> 00:55:01,557
Wanna come, boy ?.

462
00:55:01,624 --> 00:55:05,458
[ Panting ]

463
00:55:06,529 --> 00:55:08,895
Okay.

464
00:55:08,965 --> 00:55:10,956
That's okay.

465
00:55:14,003 --> 00:55:16,335
[ Yelps ]

466
00:55:17,540 --> 00:55:21,567
You missed me. I knew it.
[ Chuckling ]

467
00:55:38,494 --> 00:55:40,689
[ Whimpers ]

468
00:55:49,972 --> 00:55:51,906
The White Wolf.

469
00:56:04,487 --> 00:56:07,320
These belonged
to my brother.

470
00:56:09,325 --> 00:56:12,761
For the hunt.

471
00:56:14,263 --> 00:56:17,323
I was wrong aboutyou.

472
00:56:18,501 --> 00:56:21,163
That's okay, Lily.

473
00:56:23,572 --> 00:56:25,506
Sleep well...

474
00:56:26,709 --> 00:56:28,643
White Wolf.

475
00:56:32,848 --> 00:56:35,180
She likes me.

476
00:56:36,252 --> 00:56:38,186
She likes me, boy.

477
00:56:43,359 --> 00:56:45,827
This is tishlinjao.

478
00:56:45,895 --> 00:56:49,456
Devil's Club juice
and saltwater.

479
00:56:49,532 --> 00:56:53,400
For three days you will fast
and drink only this.

480
00:56:53,469 --> 00:56:57,565
To hunt is a sacred act.

481
00:56:57,640 --> 00:57:00,803
You must purifyyour body
to be worthy ofthe kill.

482
00:57:00,876 --> 00:57:03,470
Your mind must be clear
ofall else,

483
00:57:03,546 --> 00:57:06,413
no distractions.

484
00:57:13,155 --> 00:57:15,623
You care for Lily.

485
00:57:15,691 --> 00:57:17,659
Yes, sir, I do.

486
00:57:17,727 --> 00:57:20,525
Lily does not
yield so easily.

487
00:57:20,596 --> 00:57:24,123
- She's tough.
- All Haida women are like this,

488
00:57:24,200 --> 00:57:26,168
but Lily learned
when she was veryyoung.

489
00:57:26,235 --> 00:57:29,864
- Why's that ?.
- Already death has
visited her three times.

490
00:57:29,939 --> 00:57:34,569
Her mother, her father,
her brother.

491
00:57:34,643 --> 00:57:38,773
All taken by the smallpox,
white man's plague.

492
00:57:38,848 --> 00:57:42,340
So Lily has found
her strength.

493
00:57:42,418 --> 00:57:44,352
It is out ofyour hands,
White Wolf.

494
00:57:44,420 --> 00:57:49,119
Haida women do the choosing, and
the sun will set on top of my head...

495
00:57:49,191 --> 00:57:51,557
before Lilyyields.

496
00:57:51,627 --> 00:57:53,652
Put her out ofyour mind.

497
00:57:53,729 --> 00:57:55,754
That's not
gonna be so easy.

498
00:57:57,533 --> 00:57:59,831
Drink this.

499
00:58:02,538 --> 00:58:07,305
All the way.
Drink it all the way down.

500
00:58:07,376 --> 00:58:09,503
More.

501
00:58:09,578 --> 00:58:11,671
Thereyou go.

502
00:58:42,845 --> 00:58:44,574
[ Chuckling ]

503
00:59:05,668 --> 00:59:07,602
That's a nice shot.

504
00:59:08,704 --> 00:59:11,468
Hello !

505
00:59:11,540 --> 00:59:13,565
Who's out there ?.

506
00:59:16,612 --> 00:59:18,546
Who's out there ?.

507
00:59:22,818 --> 00:59:24,752
Was that you ?.

508
00:59:34,130 --> 00:59:36,394
I can teach you.

509
00:59:38,167 --> 00:59:40,101
Gently.

510
00:59:44,006 --> 00:59:46,804
There's nothing else
in the world...

511
00:59:46,876 --> 00:59:49,276
butyou, this arrow
and the tree.

512
00:59:49,345 --> 00:59:51,279
And you are all one.

513
00:59:53,782 --> 00:59:55,716
Let it go.

514
01:00:07,229 --> 01:00:12,223
[Man Speaking
Haida Language ]

515
01:00:12,301 --> 01:00:16,260
[Peter] We have the wolf.
Why do we need the boy ?

516
01:00:16,338 --> 01:00:18,272
[Moses ]
They're one and the same.

517
01:00:18,340 --> 01:00:20,274
[ Peter]
In the dream, it was a wolf.

518
01:00:20,342 --> 01:00:23,243
- Dreams have many shapes.
- But--

519
01:00:23,312 --> 01:00:27,146
I know. I know.
This is very hard on you, son.

520
01:00:27,216 --> 01:00:30,515
Be patient.
Your time will come.

521
01:00:31,587 --> 01:00:33,646
Your time will come.

522
01:00:47,903 --> 01:00:50,201
[ Whimpers ]

523
01:00:55,244 --> 01:00:58,441
Grandfather's bow.

524
01:01:00,916 --> 01:01:03,851
- I couldn't take this, sir.
- You will need it.

525
01:01:09,325 --> 01:01:11,623
Let Peter and Lily
come with me.

526
01:01:12,795 --> 01:01:14,729
Women don't hunt.

527
01:01:14,797 --> 01:01:16,424
Why ?.

528
01:01:16,498 --> 01:01:18,966
Old ways.

529
01:01:20,769 --> 01:01:23,704
But, Peter,
can't he go ?.

530
01:01:23,772 --> 01:01:26,263
He's ready;,
you know it.

531
01:01:26,342 --> 01:01:29,277
I will speak
to the holy man.

532
01:02:00,109 --> 01:02:02,009
How do I look ?.

533
01:02:06,148 --> 01:02:08,378
[Women Chuckling]

534
01:02:11,587 --> 01:02:15,683
[ Speaking
Haida Language ]

535
01:02:17,226 --> 01:02:20,855
[ Speaking Haida Language ]

536
01:02:26,468 --> 01:02:31,531
[ Speaking Haida Language ]

537
01:02:42,084 --> 01:02:45,576
You can go on the mountain.
You can hunt.

538
01:02:53,896 --> 01:02:58,731
[ Screaming ]

539
01:03:01,437 --> 01:03:04,895
Uncle, in the pack,
it is the femalewolfwho runs down--

540
01:03:04,973 --> 01:03:08,636
- Lily, you can't go.
- But I am betterthan Peter
with a bow. You know this.

541
01:03:08,711 --> 01:03:11,680
- Stop. My head aches.
- Who found the White Wolf ?.

542
01:03:12,915 --> 01:03:15,042
He found you.

543
01:03:17,720 --> 01:03:19,654
Moses.

544
01:03:19,722 --> 01:03:21,747
What else
did he see ?.

545
01:03:22,825 --> 01:03:24,986
One will not return.

546
01:03:30,232 --> 01:03:33,167
Whereyou come from
there are no women ?.

547
01:03:33,235 --> 01:03:35,567
You don't see them.
Only men.

548
01:03:35,637 --> 01:03:38,800
No, no. There's women.
Beautiful women.

549
01:03:38,874 --> 01:03:40,933
They're just too soft
for livin' up here.

550
01:03:41,009 --> 01:03:43,534
- Soyou want a Haida girl.
- I want Lily.

551
01:03:43,612 --> 01:03:45,546
My cousin's a princess.

552
01:03:45,614 --> 01:03:47,639
Doesn't matter to me.

553
01:03:49,118 --> 01:03:51,484
We don't buy presents.

554
01:03:51,553 --> 01:03:54,488
Ifyou want to tell a Haida girl
you care for her,

555
01:03:54,556 --> 01:03:57,821
you come up behind her,
putyour chin on her shoulder,

556
01:03:57,893 --> 01:04:00,760
and you talk softly
in her ear.

557
01:04:00,829 --> 01:04:02,763
That's it ?.

558
01:04:02,831 --> 01:04:05,766
- And she'll understand ?.
- Or breakyour nose.

559
01:04:05,834 --> 01:04:07,768
[ Chuckling ]

560
01:04:07,836 --> 01:04:11,328
You don't choose a Haida woman.
She chooses you.

561
01:04:12,775 --> 01:04:14,743
[ Speaking
Haida Language ]

562
01:04:14,810 --> 01:04:16,744
Aw, man.

563
01:04:35,697 --> 01:04:38,393
[BirdSquawking]

564
01:04:43,305 --> 01:04:46,172
[Lily]
A miner's pack.

565
01:04:53,515 --> 01:04:56,040
Mygrandfather's pole.

566
01:04:56,118 --> 01:05:00,020
It tells of
a great Haida chief.

567
01:05:01,423 --> 01:05:03,516
Bear clan.

568
01:05:05,694 --> 01:05:08,254
His father, the Wolf.

569
01:05:13,335 --> 01:05:15,269
Mother.

570
01:05:17,406 --> 01:05:20,705
Calm Woman With Fish.

571
01:05:25,814 --> 01:05:28,044
Raven.

572
01:05:29,918 --> 01:05:32,011
My father.

573
01:05:34,323 --> 01:05:38,817
To be remembered by a pole
is a great honor.

574
01:05:42,097 --> 01:05:45,999
In my clan, there have been
many chiefs and warrior women.

575
01:05:46,068 --> 01:05:48,798
I carry all of them
inside of me,

576
01:05:48,871 --> 01:05:51,806
even those
yet to be born.

577
01:05:51,874 --> 01:05:54,069
And they carry me.

578
01:05:55,711 --> 01:05:58,509
We belong
only to each other.

579
01:05:59,648 --> 01:06:02,617
And no one can
take that away from us.

580
01:06:02,684 --> 01:06:04,675
Do you understand ?.

581
01:06:04,753 --> 01:06:09,781
Since I've been here,
I've even felt that way myself.

582
01:06:09,858 --> 01:06:12,827
You know,
part of something.

583
01:06:13,896 --> 01:06:18,356
I've never felt
more at home anywhere.

584
01:06:19,468 --> 01:06:22,062
When you go back
to yourworld,

585
01:06:22,137 --> 01:06:24,833
I hope you won't forget.

586
01:06:25,908 --> 01:06:28,570
I'll never
forget you, Lily.

587
01:06:28,644 --> 01:06:31,738
I won't forget you,
White Wolf.

588
01:06:32,814 --> 01:06:35,408
The river delivered you
at my feet.

589
01:06:38,687 --> 01:06:41,485
Lily,

590
01:06:41,557 --> 01:06:43,718
there's gotta
be a way.

591
01:06:47,462 --> 01:06:49,555
What do you
want me to do ?.

592
01:06:49,631 --> 01:06:51,826
Tell me. I'll do it.

593
01:06:51,900 --> 01:06:54,835
- It's not possible.
- I wanna be with you.

594
01:06:54,903 --> 01:06:57,838
- Don't talk like that.
- I want us to be together.

595
01:06:57,906 --> 01:07:02,036
I'm LilyJoseph.
My grandfatherwas a chief.

596
01:07:02,110 --> 01:07:04,078
I will marry
one of my own.

597
01:07:04,146 --> 01:07:06,080
I wanna make this
my home.

598
01:07:06,148 --> 01:07:10,107
I wanna learn your language.
I wanna be a part ofthis with you.

599
01:07:10,185 --> 01:07:12,119
- Thatwill change.
- No, it won't.

600
01:07:12,187 --> 01:07:15,953
- You'll change.
- I'm not gonna change
how I feel aboutyou.

601
01:07:16,024 --> 01:07:17,992
You'll leave.

602
01:07:18,060 --> 01:07:20,995
It's not possible.

603
01:07:21,063 --> 01:07:23,623
- Lily.
- No.

604
01:07:23,699 --> 01:07:25,667
Lily, please.

605
01:07:27,035 --> 01:07:29,094
It's not...

606
01:07:29,171 --> 01:07:31,196
possible.

607
01:07:32,441 --> 01:07:34,568
Believe me ?.

608
01:07:39,581 --> 01:07:41,776
Believe me.

609
01:08:01,837 --> 01:08:04,738
[Bell Ringing]

610
01:08:26,662 --> 01:08:29,358
Get dressed, you pig.

611
01:08:29,431 --> 01:08:32,992
- What for ?.
- We're going to the village.

612
01:08:46,782 --> 01:08:49,580
He brought us here.

613
01:08:49,651 --> 01:08:52,347
A good sign.
Devil's Thumb.

614
01:08:59,895 --> 01:09:03,296
[Moses ] Beyond the mountain
you will find the path.

615
01:09:03,365 --> 01:09:06,630
Followit.
It will leadyou to the caribou.

616
01:09:16,411 --> 01:09:18,402
Morning, Moses.

617
01:09:20,716 --> 01:09:22,775
Walk with me, Henry.

618
01:09:22,851 --> 01:09:24,785
Have some good news.

619
01:09:24,853 --> 01:09:26,821
[ Henry ]
Yeah, what's that ?.

620
01:09:26,888 --> 01:09:29,823
Friend of mine's shipping
a load of gold to Fort Tongass.

621
01:09:29,891 --> 01:09:33,827
He needs someone to help
that we can trust. It pays $1,000.

622
01:09:33,895 --> 01:09:38,059
That's enough to getyou home and
then some, butyou have to leave today.

623
01:09:38,133 --> 01:09:41,830
I can't do that.
I gave Moses myword.

624
01:09:41,903 --> 01:09:44,929
Tomorrow White Wolfleads a hunt
to Devil's Thumb.

625
01:09:45,006 --> 01:09:47,167
White Wolf ?.

626
01:09:47,242 --> 01:09:49,369
Henry Casey.

627
01:09:53,749 --> 01:09:56,183
I'm losing my patience
with you, Henry.

628
01:09:56,251 --> 01:09:59,709
These people might think
you're something special,
but I knowyou're not.

629
01:09:59,788 --> 01:10:02,916
Now, I'm warningyou,
don't go back up that mountain.

630
01:10:02,991 --> 01:10:04,925
Warning me ?

631
01:10:04,993 --> 01:10:07,518
What kind of
religion are you ?.

632
01:10:07,596 --> 01:10:10,429
The same as you, boy.

633
01:10:10,499 --> 01:10:13,900
I don't know who you are
or what you want with these people,

634
01:10:13,969 --> 01:10:15,903
but I know
it ain't right.

635
01:10:15,971 --> 01:10:19,270
So why don't you pack up your things
and get outta here ?.

636
01:10:19,341 --> 01:10:23,573
- [ Snarling, Barking ]
- Don't show off at my expense.

637
01:10:23,645 --> 01:10:26,546
It'll come back
and hauntyou.

638
01:10:26,615 --> 01:10:30,483
- [Snarling Continues ]
- I said get outta here !

639
01:10:30,552 --> 01:10:33,521
[Barking]

640
01:10:43,431 --> 01:10:45,558
I'll pray foryou.

641
01:10:45,634 --> 01:10:49,695
[Barking]

642
01:10:59,281 --> 01:11:01,249
Get the men ready.

643
01:11:01,316 --> 01:11:03,944
The boy's going
up the mountain.

644
01:11:16,331 --> 01:11:18,458
I brought you food.

645
01:11:18,533 --> 01:11:20,330
Lily, I--

646
01:11:20,402 --> 01:11:23,030
You were in my dreams.

647
01:11:23,104 --> 01:11:25,766
- But that is where it muststop.
- Why ?.

648
01:11:25,841 --> 01:11:30,335
Because ofwho I am,
and who you are.

649
01:11:31,646 --> 01:11:33,944
That is the way it is.

650
01:12:17,759 --> 01:12:20,694
[ Peter]
Are you prepared to die ?.

651
01:12:20,762 --> 01:12:23,629
Nobody's gonna die.

652
01:12:23,698 --> 01:12:26,360
You must be ready.

653
01:12:26,434 --> 01:12:29,801
When I die, I will
come back as a raven,

654
01:12:29,871 --> 01:12:31,930
live in the forest
behind the village,

655
01:12:32,007 --> 01:12:34,976
make so much noise, no one
will be able to sleep. [ Caws ]

656
01:12:35,043 --> 01:12:37,739
[White Fang Barks ]

657
01:12:40,582 --> 01:12:42,641
[ Barks ]

658
01:12:51,960 --> 01:12:55,054
[ Growling ]

659
01:12:56,131 --> 01:12:58,395
[Twig Snaps ]

660
01:12:58,466 --> 01:13:01,094
[Limbs Crack ]

661
01:13:01,169 --> 01:13:03,103
- [Barking]
- Whoa !

662
01:13:05,140 --> 01:13:08,075
[Barking]

663
01:13:11,413 --> 01:13:14,246
White man's tricks.

664
01:13:19,821 --> 01:13:23,188
[ Yelping, Barking ]

665
01:14:01,663 --> 01:14:05,429
[ Whimpering ]

666
01:14:05,500 --> 01:14:08,094
I must cut him down.

667
01:14:13,875 --> 01:14:17,003
[Barking]

668
01:14:21,883 --> 01:14:23,851
What is it, boy ?.

669
01:14:23,918 --> 01:14:28,116
[Whimpering, Barking]

670
01:14:28,189 --> 01:14:30,316
Peter !

671
01:14:30,392 --> 01:14:34,158
[Raven Cawing]

672
01:14:35,463 --> 01:14:38,660
[ Gunshots ]

673
01:14:41,236 --> 01:14:45,002
[ Gunshots, Barking]

674
01:14:55,216 --> 01:14:57,184
I could always
outrun a horse.

675
01:14:57,252 --> 01:15:01,484
- Peter, no.
- Find the caribou.

676
01:15:01,556 --> 01:15:03,649
Peter !

677
01:15:03,725 --> 01:15:05,659
[ White Fang Whimpering]

678
01:15:14,969 --> 01:15:17,437
[ Whimpering ]

679
01:15:17,505 --> 01:15:19,666
Peter.

680
01:15:40,829 --> 01:15:42,763
[ Whinnies ]

681
01:15:57,912 --> 01:15:59,903
Whoa !

682
01:15:59,981 --> 01:16:03,382
- [ Moaning ]
- [Barking]

683
01:16:03,451 --> 01:16:06,249
[Barking Continues ]

684
01:16:20,301 --> 01:16:24,237
[ Grunting ]

685
01:16:29,144 --> 01:16:33,444
[ Explosions ]

686
01:16:34,883 --> 01:16:36,817
[ Whimpering ]

687
01:16:49,664 --> 01:16:52,098
Where's Peter ?.

688
01:16:52,167 --> 01:16:54,158
He went that way.

689
01:16:54,235 --> 01:16:56,533
Lily, you should
go get help.

690
01:16:56,604 --> 01:16:59,596
No. We stay together.

691
01:17:02,777 --> 01:17:05,041
I'm goin' with him.

692
01:17:51,793 --> 01:17:53,784
[Barking]

693
01:17:53,861 --> 01:17:57,353
[Eagle Crying]

694
01:18:21,256 --> 01:18:24,692
You found 'em, boy,
just like Moses said.

695
01:18:37,205 --> 01:18:39,571
Look.

696
01:18:39,641 --> 01:18:42,007
That's why the caribou
haven't returned.

697
01:18:42,076 --> 01:18:44,704
That wall
is blocking the pass.

698
01:18:51,386 --> 01:18:53,320
Come on.

699
01:18:53,388 --> 01:18:56,118
Let's go find out
who built it.

700
01:19:14,842 --> 01:19:16,867
[ Lily Screaming ]

701
01:19:19,814 --> 01:19:22,749
[ Screaming ]

702
01:19:23,885 --> 01:19:27,787
[ Screaming ]

703
01:19:27,855 --> 01:19:31,347
[ Groaning ]

704
01:19:33,361 --> 01:19:36,592
[ Barking ]

705
01:19:39,667 --> 01:19:41,965
Are you okay ?.

706
01:19:42,036 --> 01:19:44,004
Where are we ?.

707
01:19:45,373 --> 01:19:48,934
Looks like the air shaft
of a mine.

708
01:19:55,616 --> 01:19:57,982
Does your family
know this is here ?.

709
01:19:58,052 --> 01:20:00,816
This is a gold mine,
Lily.

710
01:20:00,888 --> 01:20:03,880
- You know what that means ?.
- Money.

711
01:20:03,958 --> 01:20:07,450
Lots of money. That's why
theywanna keepyou away from here.

712
01:20:07,528 --> 01:20:12,261
- [Men Shouting]
- We gotta get outta here,
get some help.

713
01:20:12,333 --> 01:20:14,995
The caribou will turn
and not come back.

714
01:20:15,069 --> 01:20:18,004
- We can't help that.
- We need to knock down that wall.

715
01:20:18,072 --> 01:20:21,508
- We need dynamite.
- Miners have dynamite.

716
01:20:23,711 --> 01:20:26,043
[ Clanking]

717
01:20:45,433 --> 01:20:47,526
[Thud]

718
01:20:50,638 --> 01:20:52,572
[ Rifle Cocks ]

719
01:21:04,385 --> 01:21:06,876
Now !

720
01:21:32,146 --> 01:21:35,081
[Men Talking]

721
01:21:36,951 --> 01:21:39,749
Come on.

722
01:21:39,821 --> 01:21:42,551
The hunters.

723
01:21:43,991 --> 01:21:46,619
- This way.
- [Henry] That's Heath.

724
01:21:53,968 --> 01:21:57,233
[Heath ]
Come on ! Get going !

725
01:21:57,305 --> 01:21:59,239
[ Whimpering ]

726
01:22:02,243 --> 01:22:04,177
Back to work !

727
01:22:05,313 --> 01:22:07,645
- Back !
- [ Grunts ]

728
01:22:09,183 --> 01:22:12,641
Stop ! Or I'll put a bullet
between your eyes !

729
01:22:12,720 --> 01:22:14,881
[ Guns Cock]

730
01:22:14,956 --> 01:22:18,790
Is that you, Henry ?.
Whoa.

731
01:22:30,471 --> 01:22:32,632
Congratulations.

732
01:22:32,707 --> 01:22:35,642
You're the first one
to get through.

733
01:22:35,710 --> 01:22:37,644
Get back !

734
01:22:37,712 --> 01:22:40,272
You sound
very sinister, Henry.

735
01:22:40,348 --> 01:22:44,114
I've toldyou: You and I,
we have the same religion.

736
01:22:44,185 --> 01:22:46,153
Gold.

737
01:22:46,220 --> 01:22:49,883
Who are you ?. I sure as hell know
you're not a preacher.

738
01:22:49,957 --> 01:22:54,826
No. I'm just another
greedy American, just like yourself.

739
01:22:54,896 --> 01:22:58,195
- I'm not like you.
- Oh, come on now, Henry.

740
01:23:00,001 --> 01:23:03,459
You, if anyone,
should understand.

741
01:23:04,839 --> 01:23:07,137
All this gold.

742
01:23:09,176 --> 01:23:11,235
They aren't miners.

743
01:23:11,312 --> 01:23:13,246
They never came up here.

744
01:23:13,314 --> 01:23:16,545
- Who wouldit hurt ?
- Who ?

745
01:23:16,617 --> 01:23:20,314
You starved these people
and stole from them at the same time.

746
01:23:20,388 --> 01:23:22,322
That's not the way
I plannedit.

747
01:23:22,390 --> 01:23:25,052
I thought they'd move.

748
01:23:25,126 --> 01:23:28,425
You're sick, Mister.
And you'll burn in hell.

749
01:23:28,496 --> 01:23:30,430
Harsh words, Henry.

750
01:23:30,498 --> 01:23:33,023
Very harsh words.

751
01:23:33,100 --> 01:23:36,365
But I'm not gonna letyou
turn on your own people.

752
01:23:36,437 --> 01:23:40,635
I'm prepared to offeryou a piece of
everything we take out ofthis mine...

753
01:23:40,708 --> 01:23:42,972
from here on in.

754
01:23:43,044 --> 01:23:44,978
What do ya say ?.

755
01:23:45,046 --> 01:23:47,378
It's not yours to give.

756
01:23:47,448 --> 01:23:50,178
- Well, sure it is, Henry.
- Get back !

757
01:23:50,251 --> 01:23:52,344
Do we have a deal ?.

758
01:23:53,421 --> 01:23:56,049
[ Groaning]

759
01:23:58,259 --> 01:24:00,591
Get him !

760
01:24:00,661 --> 01:24:03,186
- Get him !
- [Men Shouting]

761
01:24:03,264 --> 01:24:05,892
- Get him !
- [ Gunshots ]

762
01:24:07,335 --> 01:24:09,701
[ Barking ]

763
01:24:12,039 --> 01:24:15,873
[Barking]

764
01:24:22,316 --> 01:24:24,250
[Barking]

765
01:24:33,628 --> 01:24:37,394
[Barking]

766
01:24:38,633 --> 01:24:41,067
[Barking Continues ]

767
01:24:44,672 --> 01:24:47,334
Come on !

768
01:24:47,408 --> 01:24:49,876
- Lily !
- Go on, White Wolf!

769
01:24:51,412 --> 01:24:54,108
Go ! Go !

770
01:24:54,181 --> 01:24:56,479
[Barking]

771
01:25:14,168 --> 01:25:17,228
[ Grunting ]

772
01:25:49,570 --> 01:25:51,970
Leland ! Leland !

773
01:25:52,039 --> 01:25:53,973
Let the boy go.

774
01:25:54,041 --> 01:25:56,771
He's probably halfway
to Dawson by now to get help.

775
01:25:56,844 --> 01:25:59,711
He's got dynamite.
He'll blow the wall.

776
01:26:01,215 --> 01:26:03,274
- Get the girl.
- What ?.

777
01:26:03,350 --> 01:26:05,511
Get the girl !

778
01:26:10,357 --> 01:26:12,291
Come with me.

779
01:26:31,612 --> 01:26:33,546
Okay.

780
01:27:11,285 --> 01:27:14,186
- [ Strikes Match ]
- I got him !

781
01:27:14,255 --> 01:27:16,189
[ Gunshot ]

782
01:27:31,205 --> 01:27:33,435
